l>\n<hr/>\n<p><img alt=\"2\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2po44bx.png\"/></p>\n<ul>\n<li>1 句话能说完的，她能扯到 3 到 4 句。</li>\n<li>沟通真的很累，而且每次都是我到她位置上找他沟通(我叫她来一次，她假装没看到，然后每次都是我去)</li>\n<li>现在写的真的很难受，各位，遇到这种情况怎么办？</li>\n</ul>\n", "last_modified": 1753157483, "replies": 124, "id": 1146820}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 8377, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 1897, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 476751, "username": "MyBules", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/MyBules", "website": "joessem.com", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/08b1/fcf7/476751_mini.png?m=1644419612", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/08b1/fcf7/476751_normal.png?m=1644419612", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/08b1/fcf7/476751_large.png?m=1644419612", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/08b1/fcf7/476751_xlarge.png?m=1644419612", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/08b1/fcf7/476751_xlarge.png?m=1644419612", "created": 1584254323, "last_modified": 1644419612, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "Sivan2017", "last_touched": 1753214641, "title": "兄弟们，昨晚追尾了出租车，私了给了 1200，各位以后雨天开车小心点。", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1146817", "created": 1753153363, "deleted": 0, "content": "昨天工作比较累，意识有点模糊，而且还下暴雨，等红绿灯的时候和副驾驶说话，没注意刹车，追尾了出租车，我的车头几乎没有碰撞痕迹，对方车尾有两处凹陷，当时有点急事，对方提出私了 1200 ，我付了/(ㄒoㄒ)/~~\r\n这也是我开车以来第一次赔付，我不知道这样处理合不合适？\r\n我觉得这个私了价格有点太贵了，各位觉得呢？\r\n如果下次再追尾了别人，是直接报保险比较好，还是私了比较好？\r\n\r\n ![]( https://i.imgur.com/8DmY191.jpeg)", "content_rendered": "<p>昨天工作比较累，意识有点模糊，而且还下暴雨，等红绿灯的时候和副驾驶说话，没注意刹车，追尾了出租车，我的车头几乎没有碰撞痕迹，对方车尾有两处凹陷，当时有点急事，对方提出私了 1200 ，我付了/(ㄒoㄒ)/~~\n这也是我开车以来第一次赔付，我不知道这样处理合不合适？\n我觉得这个私了价格有点太贵了，各位觉得呢？\n如果下次再追尾了别人，是直接报保险比较好，还是私了比较好？</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8DmY191.jpeg\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1753153363, "replies": 107, "id": 1146817}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1efa/39bc/850_large.png?m=1633041301", "name": "status", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1efa/39bc/850_normal.png?m=1633041301", "title": "V2EX 站点状态", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/status", "topics": 39, "footer": "", "header": "关于 V2EX 的网站状态和功能更新的最新公告", "title_alternative": "V2EX Site Status", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1efa/39bc/850_mini.png?m=1633041301", "stars": 130, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 850, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 1, "username": "Livid", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Livid", "website": "sepia.sol.build", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "Remember the bigger green", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4ca/4238/1_mini.png?m=1753222118", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4ca/4238/1_normal.png?m=1753222118", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4ca/4238/1_large.png?m=1753222118", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4ca/4238/1_xlarge.png?m=1753222118", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4ca/4238/1_xlarge.png?m=1753222118", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4ca/4238/1_xlarge.png?m=1753222118", "created": 1272203146, "last_modified": 1753222118, "pro": 1753239305}, "last_reply_by": "AoEiuV020JP", "last_touched": 1753239279, "title": "20250722 - Solana 打赏功能更新 1", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1147010", "created": 1753222186, "deleted": 0, "content": "当你访问别人主页时，可